reviewText: Ferrell is one of the funniest
I love it!! Will Ferrell is a funny funny man and this is my favorite collection of his movies
So nice to have all these movies together!

I guess i must have just been unlucky...dvds were packaged nicely...new condition..but...both blades of glorey and night at the Roxbury had some sort of cut right throu the dvd...looks like a manufactoring problem..but those 2 dvds and unwatchable...they skip...and jump...kind of sad..only 3 watchable dvds...no point in paying to send them back for another copy...only paid 11...oh well :(
Great deal!  I love these movies.
